{
  "stem": "9230.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, it's a song-- it's not the same [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Every time when we have the memorial for high holidays, we have our cemetery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have a big monument from the Lodz Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the back, we have the names from our parents, from our brothers, little-- and every time we sing, [SINGING IN YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SOBS] A man was writing in camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he says, it will come a day and we was-- we're going to live like peaches in heaven, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's a song we always sing when everything is finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It goes [SINGING IN YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Don't say never.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You go the last way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] the heaven and the shining.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the-- the song is not written with the ink.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's written in blood and the gun is in the hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The guns that the SS was holding the-- the sticks and there was-- there was heated gas.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the song goes, the song is not written with-- in ink.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's written with blood with the gun is in the hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the gun is-- is-- is what they--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With whips.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The song is-- I have it at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I start to sing the song, I have to cry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Yiddish,yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The songs are Yiddish, and it came out from concentration camp for somebody--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Had written.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not allowed to speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they hear when we'd speak Polish, they'd throw stones on us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Put the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because, they was in the-- there was-- it was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, you know, there wasn't this side, there was now in this side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hear when we speak, we walk, everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because it was the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
